        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;1.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#304ffe;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;内存不足时&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;，无法为新的对象分配内存，自动触发&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;2.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#304ffe;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;手动请求&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;，通过 &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.19px;font-family:source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Courier New, monospace;color:#476582;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;System.gc()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt; 或 &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.19px;font-family:source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Courier New, monospace;color:#476582;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;Runtime.getRuntime().gc()&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;3.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#304ffe;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt; JVM参数&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;比如：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.19px;font-family:source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Courier New, monospace;color:#476582;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;-Xmx&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;（最大堆大小）、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.19px;font-family:source-code-pro, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas, Courier New, monospace;color:#476582;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;-Xms&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;（初始堆大小）等。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;4.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#304ffe;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;对象数量或内存使用达到阈值&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;圾收集器内部实现了一些策略，以监控对象的创建和内存使用，达到某个阈值时触发垃圾回收&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-3">
