        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;原理：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;先标记存活的对象，然后将存活的对象向一端移动，&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;覆盖掉边界的可回收内存。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;没然后直接清理掉边界以外的内存。内存会更整齐&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;缺点：移动对象会有性能开销&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br