        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;步骤：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;1、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;初始标记:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#fff23d;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;(STW)&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;，然后从GRoots&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;标记可以直接引用的&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;对象，速度很快。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;2、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;并发标记&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;不暂停线程，从已经标记过的直接引用的对象接着开始遍历整个对象，然后标记可达的对象。由于应用线程也在运行，可能会导致对象的引用被修改。所以还要&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#0000ff;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;增量标记：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;将修改了引用的对象记录到”脏卡表“中（以防止 漏标、误标）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;3、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;重新标记:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#fff23d;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;（STW）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;修正并发标记阶段遗漏/误标的对象&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;4、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;并发清理:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;遍历老年代，清除所有未被标记的对象&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;5、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;并发重置：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#000000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;重置所有的标记，为下一次CMS做准备&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-254">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="verticalAlign=middle;align=left;overflow=width;vsdxID=282;fillColor=#ffffff;gradientColor=none;shape=stencil(nZBRDoQgDERP03+WHsHFe5iISyOCQdT19kIaIxq//Jtp3zTpAFaTaUYNUkwx+F6v1EYD+AUpyRkdKCYFqACrzgf9C352LfuxyWRWg1/yhT/nRE5IsZWuZtCSK8CPeI0e/hF+jV7AJM4PO7KWCyr390bSiNtEtQM=);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=2;spacingTop=-3;spacingBottom=-3;spacingLeft=-3;spacingRight=-3;points=[];labelBackgroundColor=none;rounded=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="190" width="680" x="2419" y="3067" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;内存布局：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, Fira Sans, Droid Sans, Helvetica Neue, sans-serif;color:#2c3e50;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;1、&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;不再区分新生代和老年代为连续空间，&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;将整个堆划分为 &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;多个大小相等的 Region（默认 2048 个，每个 1~32MB）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;2、R&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;egion 类型&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;Eden Region&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;  &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;存放新创建的对象（属于新生代）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt; &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;Survivor Region  存放Minor GC 后存活的对象（属于新生代）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt; Old Region   存放长期存活的对象（老年代）&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt; Humongous Region&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;存放大对象（≥ 50% Region 大小），可能跨多个连续 Region&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-heig