        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;MixedGC:&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;使用复制算法，需要把各个region中存活的对象拷贝到别的region。&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;老年代(每经历一次YoungGC后存活下来，+1，当标志&amp;gt;阈值【默认16】，就从新生代移动到老年代)占用达到阈值（默认 45%）触发 MixedGC.清理&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;Eden + Survivor + &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;部分 Old Region&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-259">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="verticalAlign=middle;align=left;overflow=width;vsdxID=286;fillColor=#ffffff;gradientColor=none;shape=stencil(nZBRDoQgDERP03+WHsHFe5iISyOCQdT19kIaIxq//Jtp3zTpAFaTaUYNUkwx+F6v1EYD+AUpyRkdKCYFqACrzgf9C352LfuxyWRWg1/yhT/nRE5IsZWuZtCSK8CPeI0e/hF+jV7AJM4PO7KWCyr390bSiNtEtQM=);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=2;spacingTop=-3;spacingBottom=-3;spacingLeft=-3;spacingRight=-3;points=[];labelBackgroundColor=none;rounded=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="90" width="760" x="2449" y="3737" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.58px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;Full GC：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;停止系统程序，然后采用单线程进行标记、清理和压缩整理，好空闲出来一批Region来供下一次MixedGC使用，&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;这个过程是非常耗时的&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-260">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="verticalAlign=middle;align=left;overflow=width;vsdxID=288;fillColor=#ffffff;gradientColor=none;shape=stencil(nZBRDoQgDERP03+WHsHFe5iISyOCQdT19kIaIxq//Jtp3zTpAFaTaUYNUkwx+F6v1EYD+AUpyRkdKCYFqACrzgf9C352LfuxyWRWg1/yhT/nRE5IsZWuZtCSK8CPeI0e/hF+jV7AJM4PO7KWCyr390bSiNtEtQM=);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=2;spacingTop=-3;spacingBottom=-3;spacingLeft=-3;spacingRight=-3;points=[];labelBackgroundColor=none;rounded=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="90" width="760" x="2449" y="3847" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;1、初始标记：(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#0000ff;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;STW&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;),与CMS的初始标记一样&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;2、并发标记：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#4a4a4a;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;与CMS的并发标记一样&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;3、最终回收：(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#0000ff;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;STW&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;)与CMS的重新标记阶段一样&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;4、筛选回收：&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#ff0000;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;采用复制算法&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;(&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#0000ff;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;STW&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;)根据回收得到的空间大小(收益)和消耗的时间(成本)进行排序，根据用户期望的GC停顿(STW)时间来制定回收计划。【&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;G1收集器在后台维护了一个优先列表，每次根据允许的收集时间，优先选择回收价值最大的Region&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;】&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:16.49px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-261">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="verticalAlign=middle;align=left;overflow=width;vsdxID=290;fillColor=#ffffff;gradientColor=none;shape=stencil(nZBRDoQgDERP03+WHsHFe5iISyOCQdT19kIaIxq//Jtp3zTpAFaTaUYNUkwx+F6v1EYD+AUpyRkdKCYFqACrzgf9C352LfuxyWRWg1/yhT/nRE5IsZWuZtCSK8CPeI0e/hF+jV7AJM4PO7KWCyr390bSiNtEtQM=);strokeColor=#666666;strokeWidth=2;spacingTop=-3;spacingBottom=-3;spacingLeft=-3;spacingRight=-3;points=[];labelBackgroundColor=none;rounded=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="160" width="760" x="2449" y="3957" as="geometry" />
          </mxCell>
        </UserObject>
        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;操作步骤：以MixwdGC为例&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="FVv7fWHgckqN2Psue60s-262">
          <mxCell parent="1" style="verticalAlign=middle;align=center;overflow=width;vsdxID=303;fillColor=none;gradientColor=none;shape=stencil(nZBRDoQgDERP03+WHsHFe5iISyOCQdT19kIaIxq//Jtp3zTpAFaTaUYNUkwx+F6v1EYD+AUpyRkdKCYFqACrzgf9C352LfuxyWRWg1/yhT/nRE5IsZWuZtCSK8CPeI0e/hF+jV7AJM4PO7KWCyr390bSiNtEtQM=);strokeColor=none;spacingTop=-3;spacingBottom=-3;spacingLeft=-3;spacingRight=-3;points=[];labelBackgroundColor=none;rounded=0;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1">
            <mxGeometry height="30" width="220" x="2209" y="3997" as="geometry" />
