        <UserObject label="&lt;div style=&quot;font-size: 1px&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;为什么字符串常量池（String Intern Pool）从方法区（永久代）移到了 Java 堆（Heap）中&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#000010;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;？&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:思源黑体;color:#333333;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-indent:0;vertical-align:middle;direction:ltr;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;margin: 0;list-style-type: disc&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;永久代太小，大量字符串容易导致 &lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:13.19px;font-family:ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, SF Mono, Menlo, Consolas, Liberation Mono, monospace;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;OutOfMemoryError: PermGen space&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;li&gt;字符串对象本身就在堆中，把引用也放堆里更合理，便于 GC 回收&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:120%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align:left;margin-left:0;margin-right:0;margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;text-indent:0;vertical-align:middle;direction:ltr;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size:15.52px;font-family:-apple-system, blinkmacsystemfont, Helvetica Neue, helvetica, segoe ui, arial, roboto, PingFang SC, miui, Hiragino Sans GB, Microsoft Yahei, sans-serif, Source Han Serif;color:#111133;direction:ltr;letter-spacing:0px;line-height:100%;opacity:1&quot;&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" tags="Background" id="DcS866TDnodiyFPDczEb-52">
